## Next Steps

After deployment to Vercel:
1. Enable Speed Insights in the Vercel dashboard (Project → Speed Insights tab → Enable)
2. The `/_vercel/speed-insights/script.js` route will be available after deployment
3. Performance metrics will start being collected automatically
4. Data will be viewable in the Vercel dashboard after users visit the site

## Notes

- This implementation uses `@vercel/speed-insights/react` which is appropriate for React applications with Vite
